ActHazardous Products Act
PrecisOrder amending SCHEDULE I to the HAZARDOUS PRODUCTS ACT (CORDED WINDOW COVERING PRODUCTS) by including corded window covering products as defined in the Corded Window Covering Products Regulations in order to protect Canadian children against the strangulation hazard posed by corded window covering.
